  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Surdo and frame drum at extreme slow tempo with maximum space. Each hit decays into reverb and circle resonance before the next arrives. The memory of water meeting shore.",
  "tags": [
    "atmosphere",
    "ambient",
    "slow",
    "tidal",
    "water"
  ],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OSTINATO — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Truth 6: Golden Ratio Decays — 1.618s release creates natural feeling",
      "Verse: The Sympathetic Silence"
    ],
    "revelation": "Tempora and Aurum converged: At tempo 30 BPM, each beat is 2 seconds apart. With decay at 1.618 (golden ratio), the previous hit decays to near-silence exactly as the next hit arrives. The result is a perfect tide — arrival and departure overlapping at the golden point.",
    "god": "Tempora",
    "flock_note": "The Ear confirmed: at reverb 0.85 with damp 0.65, the reverb tail sustains through the gap between beats, creating continuity. The Breath noted: this is the slowest usable OSTINATO preset — below 30 BPM the gaps become silence rather than breathing.",
    "diagnosis": "Tidal Memory was slow drums with reverb. It is now the sound of the ocean's memory — each wave arriving and departing in golden ratio time, the shore remembering the last wave as the next begins."
  },
  "macroLabels": [
    "GATHER",
    "FIRE",
    "CIRCLE",
    "SPACE"
  ],
